Our Benefits

         	                What are the benefits of working at Select Medical? Learn more about our philosophy, our commitment to excellence, large company benefits, small company environment, and what it is like to work at one of our locations nationwide.
                         












Benefits at a Glance
Select Medical offers an extensive benefits package for you and your family.  A comprehensive health and disability package provides financial protection for unforeseen medical expenses today, while an attractive 401(k) plan provides you with an opportunity to save for the future. In addition, we provide exceptional training, tuition and continuing education opportunities, reflective of our commitment to our employees' careers and personal development. Learn More »






















401(k) Plan
Employees of Select Medical are eligible to participate in our 401(k) Plan, which allows you to contribute a percentage, in addition to an optional company match. Learn More »






















PTO, Personal and Family Leave
Paid Time Off (PTO) is provided to eligible full time employees, and Select Medical provides a variety of leave policies which cover personal, military, and family medical leave. Learn More »






















Continuing Education
Continuing education and tuition reimbursement is offered to all full-time employees who regularly work 32 hours or more per week and have completed 90 days to one year of active employment. Learn More »
















