Home » Careers » Hiring Process
Hiring Process











Select Medical strives to make its application process as streamlined and personal as possible.
To apply to a specific job, click on Search Jobs to begin your profile and attach your cover letter and/or resume. Your information will go directly to the recruiter.
To set up a profile without applying to a specific job opening, clink on Search Jobs and begin filling out your information. You may edit / delete / add at any time.
What Our Job Candidates Are Saying



Each interview was handled extremely professionally, everyone went out of their way to ensure I was comfortable, and I felt welcome and valued throughout the entire process.
EP, Pennsylvania



I am almost sad that my interviewing is over with Select Medical. I have met so many wonderful people, who couldn’t have been more gracious and welcoming. I heard from the Manager of Recruitment today, assuring me that she has my resume close at hand should anything cross her desk that would seem like a good fit. It was so nice of her to take the time to call me and close the loop on my time spent there.
I certainly do hope that I will end up as a member of the Select Medical Team, but regardless, it has been the most pleasurable interview experience I have ever experienced. A group of first class people all the way.Thank you for everything, your time, your warmth, and genuine interest.
Anonymous Candidate






















