PEDIATRIC ADJUSTABLE TELESCOPING SPLINT WITH SOFTGOOD – XS-M


“This splint will go to any length to prevent foot drop”

Completely adjustable, can accommodate up to 24 different foot sizes! Telescopically adjusts 3’’ in length, (7.6 cm), one size fits all, easily applied, eliminates excess inventory and lowers costs.

Moldable thermoplastic

Prevents and treats foot and ankle contractures

Suspends the heel to eliminate pressure ulcers

Anti-rotation bar included

Available with Fleece or Cool Wick® liner

Walkabout™ transfer attachment sold separately			
