About Select Medical Products
Founded in 1993, Select Medical Products has been a longstanding market leader in the orthopaedic industry as a manufacturer of Quilted CPM Pads and Ankle Foot Splints, including our patented Adjustable Telescoping Foot Splint, the only one size fits all, completely adjustable AFO available in the market.
 
We offer a wide range of products through our exclusive partnerships with the world’s top manufacturers of orthopaedic devices, including Continuous Passive Motion Machines, Upper and Lower Extremity Bracing and Graphite Halo Systems. For additional information, call 800-CPM-PADS.


































