SELECT MEDICAL INC.

















							About SMI
						



							Medical Education
						



							Course Schedules
						



							Enrollment Forms
						



							Equipment & Supplies
						






















MEDICAL EDUCATION and EQUIPMENT SOLUTIONS THAT WORK FOR YOU
Select Medical is dedicated to the highest quality medical instruction and training for those at all skill and experience levels.  Our staff of experienced American Heart Association registered medical instructors and physician directors all work within the Medical Community as licensed professionals, bringing years of hands on experience, confidence, and skills to the classroom.We provide Onsite training – saving our clients staffs both time and money.  We come to your location, offering courses at both the individual and institutional levels.  Let us provide your staff with an exceptional learning experience.  We promote a low stress, student friendly environment while providing the best and most economical courses available.  “Superior training designed to save lives”  Our company’s main charter.  In support of this charter we carry a full line of ALS monitor's and AED's.  In addition to our in-house training our knowledgeable staff can provide Onsite equipment functionality checks of your existing AED’s and ALS monitoring equipment.  We can then provide sensible recommendation's, if required, along with extremely competitive pricing.  Our goal is to promote affordable access to this life saving equipment.






 
 Promoting superior life saving equipment    and education for the good of us all.
 



Locations
Select Medical currently provides educational and project management/maintenance services in Michigan, Ohio, and Indiana - equipment sales across the U.S.Contact us @ mail@SMImedical.com 













 


 



 

 



 
SERVICES AVAILABLE 
MEDICAL EDUCATION   ...link
American Heart Association Basic Life Support (all levels), Automated External Defibrillator, First Aid, Blood-borne Pathogens, Advanced Cardiac Life Support and Pediatric Advanced Life Support courses.  12-lead ECG advanced series , Emergency Nurses Association Trauma Nurse Core Courses and Emergency Nurses Pediatric Courses, ITLS EMS continuing education courses.
EQUIPMENT and SUPPLIES   ...link
We carry a full line of Medical devices and supporting accessories to meet our costumers needs.  Product lines include Philips, Physio-Control, Zoll, and more. 
PROJECT MANAGEMENT/On-site MAINTENANCE   ...link
Our experienced staff of professional's can help develop your BLS/AED/ALS program to maximize effectiveness within your budgetary requirements.  Facility attributes, EMS co-ordination, in-service placement, signage, accessibility, security impacts are among the many criteria utilized to provide your organization with a tailored solution designed to maximize effectiveness and mitigate risk, while minimizing cost.On-site maintenance contracts available. 
 

















 

 














