Select Medical Corp: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















select medical corp
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Health Care Facilities & Svcs
Sub-Industry: Health Care Facilities
Select Medical Corporation provides healthcare services. The Company offers long term care for critically ill patients, as well as inpatient and outpatient, rehabilitation therapy and recovery services to patients suffering from trauma and other serious conditions. Select Medical serves patients throughout the United States.




